			Company Description 


			WRIT Media Group, Inc. produces films, television programs and similar entertainment programs for various media formats. It is a content creation company which intends to produce, acquire and distribute live concerts in 3D for initial worldwide digital broadcast into digitally-enabled movie theaters...
		


                WRIT Media Group, Inc. produces films, television programs and similar entertainment programs for various media formats. It is a content creation company which intends to produce, acquire and distribute live concerts in 3D for initial worldwide digital broadcast into digitally-enabled movie theaters. The company was founded by Tal Leon Kapelner, Glenn M. Benest and Ariella Kapelner on March 9, 2007 and is headquartered in Beverly Hills, CA.
            




